## Installation

```sh
pip install clite
```

## Usage

### Example

```python
from clite import Clite

app = Clite(
    name="myapp",
    description="A small package for creating command line interfaces",
)

@app.command()
def hello(name: str = "world"):
    print(f"Hello, {name}!")

if __name__ == "__main__":
    app()
```

### Run it

```sh
python main.py hello Alice
```

Output:

```
Hello, Alice!
```

